             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HP has made the following software updates available to resolve these
vulnerabilities. HP Version Control Agent 7.3.3.0 for Linux and Windows is
available from the following locations:

HP Version Control Agent (VCA) for Windows x86 v7.3.3.0

http://www.hp.com/swpublishing/MTX-8aefeaf490284a7691eca97d13

HP Version Control Agent (VCA) for Windows x64 v7.3.3.0

http://www.hp.com/swpublishing/MTX-c0d32bac154a4d93839d8cd1f2

HP Version Control Agent (VCA) for Linux v7.3.3-0

http://www.hp.com/swpublishing/MTX-8208c3987b1b4a5093f3e8fcc3

